Package jcolibri.cbrcore.event

Interface Summary
RegistryChangeListener Interface to be implemented by registry change listeners, to react when a RegistryChangeEvent is retrieved.
StateChangeListener Interface to be implemented by atate change listeners, to react when a StateChangeEvent is retrieved.
TaskChangeListener Interface to be implemented by task change listeners, to react when a TaskChangeEvent is retrieved.
 

Class Summary
RegistryChangeEvent Event to be launched when a change on a registry is detected.
StateChangeEvent Event to be launched when a change on the state of the CBR system is detected.
TaskChangeEvent Event to be launched when a change on the state of the CBR system is detected.
